Company Overview of Avalon Global Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Avalon Global Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the public equity markets of developed countries. The firm invests in growth stocks of mid to large cap companies to create its portfolios. It uses long/short equity and margin leverage strategies to manage its investments. The firm obtains external research to complement its in-house research.  It focuses its investments in five sectors including consumer goods, retailing, health-care, technology, and media and related services. Avalon Global Asset Management, LLC was founded in November 1999 and is based in San Francisco, Califor...
Avalon Global Asset Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in the public equity markets of developed countries. The firm invests in growth stocks of mid to large cap companies to create its portfolios. It uses long/short equity and margin leverage strategies to manage its investments. The firm obtains external research to complement its in-house research.  It focuses its investments in five sectors including consumer goods, retailing, health-care, technology, and media and related services. Avalon Global Asset Management, LLC was founded in November 1999 and is based in San Francisco, California.
Detailed Description


